<h1>[Notesapp] Main Page</h1>
<p>[Notesapp] is a web app that allows you to save notes online, without requiring an account.</p>
<p>This app is not intended to be used for confidential information, anybody who knows the unique key for your notepad will be able to view and edit it freely.</p>
<p>Try to pick an identifier only you would think of!</p>

<%= form_for @notepad do |f| %>
  <p>
    <%= f.label "Enter the Notepad Identifier:" %><br>
    <%= f.text_field :url, :value => @notepad.url%>
  </p>

  <p>
    <%= f.submit "Go"%>
  </p>
<% end %>
